Interface RoutingModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseRoutingModel, Serializable

    public interface RoutingModel
extends BaseRoutingModel
    Used to define new routing model that can be used in the operator mode to get questions for the processing.

        Gets a next question for the operator mode.

        con - the current connection
        operatorId - the operator id
        operator - the operator
        responsibility - the question will be got from the subprojects
        languages - languages the operator may process
        doctypes - doc types the operator may process
        nDays - the number of the days the mails are at least old and not completed ( Project.getNotification()). Used by the notification call.
        nCustomerId - the customer id. Used by the notification call.
        nQuestionDate - the question date. Used by the notification call.
        role - the operator role
